aa(lp16
VAnd by definition, every one of you who is in this room
p17
aVmust consider yourself a global soul,
p18
aVa global citizen.
p19
aVYou work on the front lines. And you've seen the best and the worst
p20
aVthat human beings can do for one another and to one another.
