aa(lp219
VLifespring Hospital
p220
aVis a joint venture between Acumen and the government of India
p221
aVto bring quality, affordable maternal health care
p222
aVto low-income women,
p223
aVand it's been so successful that it's currently building
p224
aVa new hospital every 35 days.
p225
aa(lp226
VAnd 1298 Ambulances decided that it was going to
p227
aVreinvent a completely broken industry,
p228
aVbuilding an ambulance service in Bombay
p229
aVthat would use the technology of Google Earth,
p230
aVa sliding scale pricing system
p231
aVso that all people could have access,
p232
aVand a severe and public decision
p233
aVnot to engage in any form of corruption.
p234
aVSo that in the terrorist attacks of November
